<!-- ═══════════════════ 3. 正向传播细节 ═══════════════════ -->
<section id="forward">
<h2>3. 正向传播：逐阶段张量变换</h2>

<h3>3.1 SigLIP 视觉编码</h3>
<div class="note">
  <strong>文件：</strong><code>src/openpi/models/siglip.py</code> &nbsp;·&nbsp;
  变体 <code>So400m/14</code>：27 层，1152 维，16 头，Patch=14
</div>
<pre>
<span class="cm"># 输入：归一化到 [-1,1] 的 RGB 图像</span>
image                <span class="shape">[B, 224, 224, 3]</span>

<span class="cm"># ① Patch Embedding — Conv2D(stride=14)</span>
patch_embed          <span class="shape">[B, 16, 16, 1152]</span>  <span class="cm"># 224/14=16 个 patch</span>
reshape              <span class="shape">[B, 256, 1152]</span>     <span class="cm"># 16×16=256 个 token</span>

<span class="cm"># ② 加 sin-cos 2D 位置编码</span>
tokens + posemb      <span class="shape">[B, 256, 1152]</span>

<span class="cm"># ③ 27 层 ViT Transformer（LayerNorm-first）</span>
<span class="cm">#    MHSA(16 heads) + MLP(4×1152) + Dropout + Residual</span>
vit_output           <span class="shape">[B, 256, 1152]</span>     <span class="cm"># pool_type="none"，保留所有 token</span>
</pre>
<span class="ref">siglip.py:208-290 — 每张图像独立编码，3 路并行，不共享权重</span>

<h3>3.2 Prefix 嵌入拼接（embed_prefix）</h3>
<pre>
<span class="cm"># 3 路图像 token（1152-dim → PaliGemma LLM 输入需 2048-dim）</span>
<span class="cm"># SigLIP 输出直接作为 PaliGemma 的 image tokens（内部已有投影层）</span>
img_base        <span class="shape">[B, 256, 1152]</span>  ar_mask = <span class="num">False</span> × 256
img_left_wrist  <span class="shape">[B, 256, 1152]</span>  ar_mask = <span class="num">False</span> × 256
img_right_wrist <span class="shape">[B, 256, 1152]</span>  ar_mask = <span class="num">False</span> × 256

<span class="cm"># 语言 token 嵌入（Gemma Embedder）</span>
tokenized_prompt  <span class="shape">[B, 48]</span>
→ embed_table[vocab=257152, 2048] + scale√2048
→ lang_emb        <span class="shape">[B, 48, 2048]</span>  ar_mask = <span class="num">False</span> × 48

<span class="cm"># 拼接所有 Prefix token</span>
prefix_tokens = concat([img×3, lang_emb], axis=1)
                <span class="shape">[B, 816, 2048]</span>   <span class="cm"># 256×3 + 48 = 816</span>
prefix_ar_mask  <span class="shape">[816]</span>           <span class="cm"># 全 False（双向全注意力）</span>
</pre>
<span class="ref">pi0.py:106-137</span>

<h3>3.3 Suffix 嵌入拼接（embed_suffix）</h3>
<pre>
<span class="cm"># ① 状态 token</span>
obs.state       <span class="shape">[B, 32]</span>
→ state_proj    Linear(32→2048)
→ state_token   <span class="shape">[B, 1, 2048]</span>    ar_mask = <span class="tp">True</span>  <span class="cm"># 因果边界起点</span>

<span class="cm"># ② 加噪动作 token</span>
x_t             <span class="shape">[B, 50, 32]</span>    <span class="cm"># flow matching 加噪后的动作</span>
→ action_in_proj  Linear(32→2048)
→ action_tokens <span class="shape">[B, 50, 2048]</span>

<span class="cm"># ③ 时间步嵌入（sin-cos 位置编码）</span>
t               <span class="shape">[B]</span>             <span class="cm"># ∈ [0.001, 0.999]</span>
→ posemb_sincos(t, dim=2048, min_period=4e-3, max_period=4.0)
→ time_emb      <span class="shape">[B, 2048]</span>
→ broadcast to  <span class="shape">[B, 50, 2048]</span>

<span class="cm"># ④ Action-Time MLP（π₀ 非 pi05 模式）</span>
concat([action_tokens, time_emb], axis=-1)  <span class="shape">[B, 50, 4096]</span>
→ Linear(4096→2048) → Swish → Linear(2048→2048)
→ action_time_tokens                        <span class="shape">[B, 50, 2048]</span>

<span class="cm"># ⑤ 拼接 Suffix</span>
suffix_tokens = concat([state_token, action_time_tokens], axis=1)
              <span class="shape">[B, 51, 2048]</span>
suffix_ar_mask  <span class="shape">[51]</span>  = [True, False×50]  <span class="cm"># 只有 state 是边界</span>
</pre>
<span class="ref">pi0.py:140-186 &nbsp;|&nbsp; pi05 模式下 AdaRMSNorm 接收 time_emb 作为调制信号</span>
</section>

<!-- ═══════════════════ 4. 注意力掩码 ═══════════════════ -->
<section id="attention">
<h2>4. Prefix-Suffix 注意力掩码机制</h2>

<div class="note">
  <strong>核心思想：</strong>Prefix（图像+语言）内部互相可见（双向），Suffix（状态+动作）内部因果有序，
  但 Suffix 不能回看 Prefix，Prefix 也不能看到 Suffix。两路 Expert 共享同一套 Transformer 权重。
</div>

<h3>4.1 掩码构造逻辑</h3>
<pre>
<span class="cm"># make_attn_mask(input_mask, mask_ar)  — pi0.py:19-44</span>
input_mask  <span class="shape">[B, 867]</span>  <span class="cm"># True=有效token，False=padding</span>
mask_ar     <span class="shape">[867]</span>    <span class="cm"># True=此位置是因果组边界</span>

<span class="cm"># mask_ar 具体值（以 π₀ 典型配置为例）：</span>
<span class="cm"># [False×816(prefix),  True(state),  False×50(actions)]</span>
<span class="cm">#  ^—— prefix 无边界 ——^  ^—— suffix 在 state 处起边界 ——^</span>

cumsum = jnp.cumsum(mask_ar, axis=1)
<span class="cm"># prefix 区域 cumsum=0, state 位置 cumsum=1, action 位置 cumsum=1</span>

<span class="cm"># token i 能看到 token j 当且仅当：cumsum[j] <= cumsum[i]</span>
attn_mask[b,i,j] = (cumsum[j] <= cumsum[i]) AND (input_mask[b,j])

<span class="cm"># 最终掩码形状</span>
attn_mask  <span class="shape">[B, 867, 867]</span>
</pre>

<h3>4.2 注意力可见性矩阵</h3>
<div class="dw">
  <div class="dh"><span>哪些 token 能看到哪些 token</span></div>
  <div class="db">
    <table>
      <thead>
        <tr><th>查询方 (Q)</th><th>能看到 Prefix 图像</th><th>能看到语言 token</th><th>能看到 state token</th><th>能看到 action token</th></tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr><td>Prefix 图像 token</td><td style="color:var(--green)">✓ 全双向</td><td style="color:var(--green)">✓</td><td style="color:var(--red)">✗</td><td style="color:var(--red)">✗</td></tr>
        <tr><td>语言 token</td><td style="color:var(--green)">✓</td><td style="color:var(--green)">✓ 全双向</td><td style="color:var(--red)">✗</td><td style="color:var(--red)">✗</td></tr>
        <tr><td>state token</td><td style="color:var(--red)">✗</td><td style="color:var(--red)">✗</td><td style="color:var(--green)">✓ 自身</td><td style="color:var(--red)">✗</td></tr>
        <tr><td>action[i] token</td><td style="color:var(--red)">✗</td><td style="color:var(--red)">✗</td><td style="color:var(--green)">✓ state</td><td style="color:var(--green)">✓ action[0..i]</td></tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="warn">
  <strong>为什么 Suffix 不能看 Prefix？</strong>
  训练时 Prefix（观测）信息只作为背景条件，通过 KV Cache 缓存，
  推理时只需对 Suffix 做 cross-attention 到缓存好的 Prefix KV，
  避免动作序列直接参与 Prefix 的反向传播。
</div>

<h3>4.3 Transformer 内部：双 Expert 如何共享权重</h3>
<pre>
<span class="cm"># gemma.py:389-411 — Module.__call__</span>
<span class="cm"># 两路输入在拼接后共同进入同一套 Transformer 权重</span>

embedded = [prefix_tokens, suffix_tokens]
<span class="cm"># prefix: [B, 816, 2048]  |  suffix: [B, 51, 2048]</span>

<span class="cm"># 在 attention 内部合并为一个序列（pi0.py:209 传入 list）</span>
<span class="cm"># gemma.py 内部对 list 做 jnp.concatenate → [B, 867, 2048]</span>
x_all = concat([prefix, suffix], axis=1)  <span class="cm"># [B, 867, 2048]</span>

<span class="cm"># 共享 Q/K/V 投影权重（每层一套）</span>
q, k, v = qkv_einsum(<span class="st">"BSD,3KDH->3BSKH"</span>, x_all)
<span class="cm"># 每个: [B, 867, num_kv_heads=1, heads=8, head_dim=256]</span>

<span class="cm"># RoPE 旋转位置编码（基于 positions 绝对位置）</span>
q = apply_rope(q, positions)  <span class="cm"># [B, 867, 8, 256]</span>
k = apply_rope(k, positions)

<span class="cm"># GQA 注意力（8:1 head ratio）</span>
logits = einsum(<span class="st">"BTKGH, BSKH -> BKGTS"</span>, q, k)  <span class="cm"># [B,1,8,867,867]</span>
logits = where(attn_mask, logits, <span class="num">-inf</span>)
probs  = softmax(logits, axis=-1)
out    = einsum(<span class="st">"BKGTS, BSKH -> BTKGH"</span>, probs, v)  <span class="cm"># [B,867,1,8,256]</span>
out    = reshape → <span class="shape">[B, 867, 8, 256]</span> → proj → <span class="shape">[B, 867, 2048]</span>

<span class="cm"># 最后分离出两路输出</span>
prefix_out = out[:, :816, :]   <span class="shape">[B, 816, 2048]</span>
suffix_out = out[:, 816:, :]   <span class="shape">[B, 51, 2048]</span>
</pre>
<span class="ref">gemma.py:158-250（Attention）, 284-333（Block）, 389-411（Module）</span>

<h3>4.4 Gemma 每层 FFN 结构（GeGLU 变体）</h3>
<pre>
x_norm = RMSNorm(x)                                     <span class="shape">[B, T, 2048]</span>

gate   = Linear_gate(x_norm)  → GELU                   <span class="shape">[B, T, 16384]</span>
up     = Linear_up(x_norm)                              <span class="shape">[B, T, 16384]</span>
hidden = gate * up                                      <span class="shape">[B, T, 16384]</span>
out    = Linear_down(hidden)                            <span class="shape">[B, T, 2048]</span>

x = x + out  <span class="cm"># Residual</span>
</pre>
</section>

<!-- ═══════════════════ 5. Flow Matching ═══════════════════ -->
<section id="flow">
<h2>5. Flow Matching：如何学习动作生成</h2>

<h3>5.1 训练期：加噪与损失</h3>
<div class="dw">
  <div class="dh"><span>Flow Matching 训练步</span><span class="tag">pi0.py:189-214</span></div>
  <div class="db">
    <div class="mermaid">
%%{init:{'theme':'dark','flowchart':{'curve':'basis','padding':14}}}%%
flowchart LR
    A["目标动作 actions\n[B, 50, 32]"]
    B["高斯噪声 ε\n[B, 50, 32]\n~N(0,I)"]
    T["时间步 t\n[B]\n~Beta(1.5,1)×0.999+0.001"]

    C["线性插值加噪\nx_t = t·ε + (1-t)·actions\n[B, 50, 32]"]
    D["速度场目标\nu_t = ε - actions\n[B, 50, 32]"]

    E["模型前向传播\nPaliGemma + Action Expert\nInput: x_t, t, obs"]
    F["预测速度场 v_t\naction_out_proj\n[B, 50, 32]"]

    G["MSE Loss\nmean((v_t - u_t)²)\n→ [B,50] → 标量"]

    A --> C & D
    B --> C & D
    T --> C
    C --> E
    T --> E
    E --> F
    F --> G
    D --> G

    style E fill:#1a2035,stroke:#39c5cf,color:#c9d1d9
    style G fill:#1a2035,stroke:#f85149,color:#c9d1d9
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<pre>
<span class="cm"># pi0.py:189-214 完整 compute_loss</span>
<span class="kw">def</span> <span class="fn">compute_loss</span>(rng, observation, actions, *, train=<span class="tp">False</span>):
    preprocess_rng, noise_rng, time_rng = jax.random.split(rng, <span class="num">3</span>)
    observation = preprocess_observation(preprocess_rng, observation, train=train)

    noise = jax.random.normal(noise_rng, actions.shape)         <span class="cm"># [B, 50, 32]</span>
    time  = jax.random.beta(time_rng, <span class="num">1.5</span>, <span class="num">1</span>, batch_shape)       <span class="cm"># [B]</span>
    time  = time * <span class="num">0.999</span> + <span class="num">0.001</span>                               <span class="cm"># ∈ [0.001, 0.999]</span>

    x_t = time[...,<span class="kw">None</span>,<span class="kw">None</span>] * noise + (<span class="num">1</span> - time[...,<span class="kw">None</span>,<span class="kw">None</span>]) * actions
    u_t = noise - actions                                        <span class="cm"># 真实速度方向</span>

    prefix_tokens, prefix_mask, prefix_ar_mask = embed_prefix(observation)
    suffix_tokens, suffix_mask, suffix_ar_mask, _ = embed_suffix(observation, x_t, time)

    <span class="cm"># 拼接掩码 → [B, 867, 867]</span>
    attn_mask = make_attn_mask(
        concat([prefix_mask, suffix_mask], axis=<span class="num">1</span>),
        concat([prefix_ar_mask, suffix_ar_mask], axis=<span class="num">0</span>)
    )
    positions = cumsum(input_mask, axis=<span class="num">1</span>) - <span class="num">1</span>

    (_, suffix_out), _ = PaliGemma.llm(
        [prefix_tokens, suffix_tokens], mask=attn_mask, positions=positions
    )                                                            <span class="cm"># suffix_out: [B,51,2048]</span>

    v_t = action_out_proj(suffix_out[:, <span class="num">-50</span>:])                  <span class="cm"># [B, 50, 32]</span>
    <span class="kw">return</span> jnp.mean(jnp.square(v_t - u_t), axis=-<span class="num">1</span>)             <span class="cm"># [B, 50]</span>
</pre>

<div class="note">
  <strong>Beta(1.5, 1) 时间步分布的意义：</strong>偏向 t→0（靠近目标动作端），
  使网络在接近干净动作的区域多训练，类似于 EDM 的加权采样策略，提升生成质量。
</div>

<h3>5.2 π₀.₅ 的 AdaRMSNorm 调制（pi05 分支）</h3>
<pre>
<span class="cm"># pi05=True 时，时间步不再通过 Action-Time MLP 注入，</span>
<span class="cm"># 而是通过 AdaRMSNorm 调制每层 Transformer 的归一化</span>

time_emb = posemb_sincos(t, dim=2048)   <span class="cm"># [B, 2048]</span>
adarms_cond = time_emb                  <span class="cm"># 传入 PaliGemma.llm 的 suffix expert</span>

<span class="cm"># 在 AdaRMSNorm 内部（gemma.py）：</span>
scale, shift, gate = Dense(3 * d_model)(adarms_cond)  <span class="cm"># [B, 2048] × 3</span>
x_norm = RMSNorm(x)
x_mod  = x_norm * (1 + scale[:, None, :]) + shift[:, None, :]
<span class="cm"># gate 用于 residual 缩放</span>
</pre>
<span class="ref">pi0.py:162-178（pi05 分支）</span>

<h3>5.3 π₀-FAST：自回归 Cross-Entropy 替代方案</h3>
<pre>
<span class="cm"># pi0_fast.py:198-233</span>
<span class="cm"># 动作先用 FAST tokenizer 离散化</span>
action_tokens_ids  <span class="shape">[B, T_action]</span>  <span class="cm"># int32, vocab内的动作token</span>

<span class="cm"># 送入 PaliGemma 做 causal LM</span>
logits = model(observation, tokenized_prompt)  <span class="shape">[B, T_total, vocab_size]</span>

<span class="cm"># 只对动作部分计算 CE loss</span>
targets   = one_hot(prompt[:, 1:], vocab_size)           <span class="shape">[B, T-1, V]</span>
logp      = log_softmax(logits, axis=-1)
token_loss = -sum(targets * logp, axis=-1)               <span class="shape">[B, T-1]</span>
loss      = sum(token_loss * loss_mask) / sum(loss_mask) <span class="cm"># 只算动作 token</span>
</pre>
</section>

<!-- ═══════════════════ 6. 训练循环 ═══════════════════ -->
<section id="train-loop">
<h2>6. 训练循环：从 train.py 到 JAX 梯度更新</h2>

<h3>6.1 完整调用链</h3>
<div class="flow-chain">
  <div class="fc-box">main(config)</div><div class="fc-arr">→</div>
  <div class="fc-box">jax.jit(train_step)</div><div class="fc-arr">→</div>
  <div class="fc-box">nnx.value_and_grad(loss_fn)</div><div class="fc-arr">→</div>
  <div class="fc-box">model.compute_loss()</div><div class="fc-arr">→</div>
  <div class="fc-box">jnp.mean(chunked_loss)</div><div class="fc-arr">→</div>
  <div class="fc-box">grads</div><div class="fc-arr">→</div>
  <div class="fc-box">AdamW.update()</div><div class="fc-arr">→</div>
  <div class="fc-box">optax.apply_updates()</div><div class="fc-arr">→</div>
  <div class="fc-box">EMA update</div>
</div>

<h3>6.2 训练步核心代码</h3>
<pre>
<span class="cm"># train.py:137-191</span>
<span class="kw">def</span> <span class="fn">train_step</span>(config, rng, state, batch):
    model = nnx.merge(state.model_def, state.params)
    model.train()  <span class="cm"># 开启 dropout 等训练行为</span>

    <span class="kw">def</span> <span class="fn">loss_fn</span>(model, rng, observation, actions):
        chunked_loss = model.compute_loss(rng, observation, actions, train=<span class="tp">True</span>)
        <span class="cm"># chunked_loss: [B, 50]（每个 action horizon 步的 MSE）</span>
        <span class="kw">return</span> jnp.mean(chunked_loss)  <span class="cm"># 标量</span>

    train_rng = jax.random.fold_in(rng, state.step)  <span class="cm"># 每步不同随机数</span>
    observation, actions = batch

    <span class="cm"># ① 计算 loss 和梯度（只对 trainable 参数求导）</span>
    diff_state = nnx.DiffState(<span class="num">0</span>, config.trainable_filter)
    loss, grads = nnx.value_and_grad(loss_fn, argnums=diff_state)(
        model, train_rng, observation, actions
    )

    <span class="cm"># ② AdamW 更新</span>
    params     = state.params.filter(config.trainable_filter)
    updates, new_opt_state = state.tx.update(grads, state.opt_state, params)
    new_params = optax.apply_updates(params, updates)

    <span class="cm"># ③ 写回 NNX 模型</span>
    nnx.update(model, new_params)
    new_params = nnx.state(model)

    <span class="cm"># ④ EMA 影子参数更新（decay=0.99）</span>
    <span class="kw">if</span> state.ema_decay <span class="kw">is not</span> <span class="tp">None</span>:
        ema = jax.tree.map(
            <span class="kw">lambda</span> old, new: state.ema_decay * old + (<span class="num">1</span> - state.ema_decay) * new,
            state.ema_params, new_params
        )

    <span class="cm"># 诊断指标</span>
    info = {
        <span class="st">"loss"</span>:       loss,
        <span class="st">"grad_norm"</span>:  optax.global_norm(grads),       <span class="cm"># 梯度全局范数</span>
        <span class="st">"param_norm"</span>: optax.global_norm(kernel_params), <span class="cm"># 参数范数（2D以上）</span>
    }
    <span class="kw">return</span> new_state, info
</pre>

<h3>6.3 AdamW 优化器配置</h3>
<pre>
<span class="cm"># optimizer.py — AdamW 链式组合</span>
tx = optax.chain(
    optax.clip_by_global_norm(<span class="num">1.0</span>),    <span class="cm"># 梯度裁剪（防爆炸）</span>
    optax.adamw(
        learning_rate = lr_schedule,   <span class="cm"># 见下方</span>
        b1 = <span class="num">0.9</span>,
        b2 = <span class="num">0.95</span>,
        eps = <span class="num">1e-8</span>,
        weight_decay = <span class="num">1e-10</span>,          <span class="cm"># 约等于无</span>
    )
)

<span class="cm"># Cosine Decay 学习率（以 π₀.₅ LIBERO 配置为例）</span>
lr_schedule = CosineDecaySchedule(
    warmup_steps = <span class="num">10_000</span>,   <span class="cm"># 线性 warmup</span>
    peak_lr      = <span class="num">5e-5</span>,
    decay_steps  = <span class="num">1_000_000</span>,
    decay_lr     = <span class="num">5e-5</span>,     <span class="cm"># 末尾保持（不衰减至 0）</span>
)
<span class="cm"># π₀ 默认：warmup=1000, peak=2.5e-5, decay_steps=30000</span>
</pre>

<h3>6.4 训练状态结构</h3>
<pre>
TrainState:
  step         int                  <span class="cm"># 当前步数</span>
  params       NNX State            <span class="cm"># 模型参数（含 frozen，冻结的转 bfloat16）</span>
  model_def    NNX GraphDef         <span class="cm"># 模型图结构（不序列化）</span>
  tx           optax.GradientTx     <span class="cm"># 优化器定义（不序列化）</span>
  opt_state    optax.OptState       <span class="cm"># AdamW 动量状态 (m, v)</span>
  ema_decay    float | None         <span class="cm"># EMA 系数，None=关闭</span>
  ema_params   NNX State | None     <span class="cm"># EMA 影子参数</span>
</pre>
</section>

