<!-- ═══════════════════ 8. 推理解码 ═══════════════════ -->
<section id="inference">
<h2>8. 推理期：KV Cache + 迭代去噪</h2>

<h3>8.1 两阶段推理</h3>
<div class="two-col">
<div>
<h4>阶段①：Prefix Prefill（只做一次）</h4>
<pre>
<span class="cm"># pi0.py:234-237</span>
prefix_tokens, prefix_mask, prefix_ar_mask = embed_prefix(obs)
prefix_attn_mask = make_attn_mask(prefix_mask, prefix_ar_mask)
positions = cumsum(prefix_mask) - <span class="num">1</span>

<span class="cm"># 只对 prefix 做前向，返回每层 KV cache</span>
_, kv_cache = PaliGemma.llm(
    [prefix_tokens, <span class="kw">None</span>],
    mask=prefix_attn_mask,
    positions=positions
)
<span class="cm"># kv_cache: 18层 × (K [B,816,8,256], V [B,816,8,256])</span>
</pre>
</div>
<div>
<h4>阶段②：迭代去噪（num_steps=10 次）</h4>
<pre>
x_t = noise ~ N(0,I)    <span class="cm"># [B, 50, 32], t=1.0</span>
dt = <span class="num">-0.1</span>               <span class="cm"># 每步 Δt</span>

<span class="kw">for</span> step in range(<span class="num">10</span>):  <span class="cm"># t: 1.0 → 0.1</span>
    suffix_tokens, ... = embed_suffix(obs, x_t, t)
    <span class="cm"># 构造 cross-attn mask: suffix → prefix KV cache</span>
    full_mask = concat([prefix_mask, suffix_mask], axis=-<span class="num">1</span>)
    <span class="cm"># [B, 51, 867]</span>

    (_, suffix_out), _ = PaliGemma.llm(
        [<span class="kw">None</span>, suffix_tokens],
        mask=full_mask,
        kv_cache=kv_cache,   <span class="cm"># 复用 prefix 缓存</span>
    )
    v_t = action_out_proj(suffix_out[:, <span class="num">-50</span>:])  <span class="cm"># [B,50,32]</span>

    <span class="cm"># Euler ODE step：沿速度场方向走一步</span>
    x_t = x_t + dt * v_t
    t   = t + dt

<span class="kw">return</span> x_t  <span class="cm"># [B, 50, 32] 最终动作</span>
</pre>
</div>
</div>

<div class="note">
  <strong>KV Cache 加速原理：</strong>
  Prefix（图像+语言，816 个 token）的 Key/Value 在每次动作生成时是固定的，
  只需计算一次并缓存。每次去噪迭代只需对 51 个 Suffix token 做计算，
  再通过 cross-attention 查询缓存好的 Prefix KV。
  整体推理复杂度从 O(867²) × 10 次降低到 O(816²) + O(51 × 867) × 10 次。
</div>
</section>

