<h3>9.4 蒸馏 Loss 完整实现</h3>
<pre>
<span class="cm"># pi0_pytorch.py:520-585 — DistilledPI0Pytorch.forward()</span>
<span class="kw">def</span> <span class="fn">forward</span>(self, observation, actions, teacher: PI0Pytorch, noise=<span class="tp">None</span>, time=<span class="tp">None</span>):

    <span class="cm"># ① 采样噪声和时间步（两模型共享相同噪声！）</span>
    noise = self.sample_noise(actions.shape, device)     <span class="cm"># [B, 50, 32]</span>
    time  = self.sample_time(actions.shape[<span class="num">0</span>], device)   <span class="cm"># [B] ~ Beta(1.5,1)</span>

    x_t = time[...,<span class="kw">None</span>,<span class="kw">None</span>] * noise + (<span class="num">1</span> - time[...,<span class="kw">None</span>,<span class="kw">None</span>]) * actions
    u_t = noise - actions                                <span class="cm"># GT 速度场 [B, 50, 32]</span>

    <span class="cm"># ② Teacher 前向（冻结，不计算梯度）</span>
    <span class="kw">with</span> torch.no_grad():
        v_t_teacher = teacher.eval_model(observation, actions, noise, time)
        <span class="cm"># v_t_teacher: [B, 50, 32]  Teacher 预测的速度场</span>

    <span class="cm"># ③ Student 前向（完整前向，需要梯度）</span>
    prefix_embs, prefix_pad, prefix_att = self.embed_prefix(images, ...)
    suffix_embs, suffix_pad, suffix_att, adarms = self.embed_suffix(state, x_t, time)

    att_2d = make_att_2d_masks(...)   <span class="cm"># [B, 867, 867]（6层 Transformer）</span>
    (_, suffix_out), _ = self.paligemma_with_expert.forward(
        inputs_embeds=[prefix_embs, suffix_embs],
        attention_mask=att_2d, ...
    )

    v_t = self.action_out_proj(suffix_out[:, <span class="num">-50</span>:])      <span class="cm"># [B, 50, 32]</span>

    <span class="cm"># ④ 双重 MSE Loss</span>
    loss_gt      = F.mse_loss(u_t, v_t)          <span class="cm"># 与真实速度场对齐</span>
    loss_distill = F.mse_loss(v_t_teacher, v_t)  <span class="cm"># 向 Teacher 输出靠拢</span>

    <span class="kw">return</span> loss_gt + loss_distill                 <span class="cm"># 等权相加（各 1.0）</span>
</pre>

<div class="warn">
  <strong>注意：</strong><code>DistilledPi0Config</code> 中定义了 <code>loss_weight_gt</code> 和
  <code>loss_weight_teacher</code> 字段，但当前 <code>forward()</code> 实现中
  <b>并未使用这两个权重</b>——始终硬编码为等权相加。
  如需调整比例，需手动修改 <code>pi0_pytorch.py:582-583</code>。
  <span class="ref">pi0_pytorch.py:582</span>
</div>

<h3>9.5 训练循环集成</h3>
<pre>
<span class="cm"># train_pytorch.py:566-656 — 蒸馏训练主循环</span>
<span class="kw">while</span> global_step &lt; config.num_train_steps:
    <span class="kw">for</span> observation, actions <span class="kw">in</span> loader:

        <span class="cm"># 更新学习率</span>
        <span class="kw">for</span> pg <span class="kw">in</span> optim.param_groups:
            pg[<span class="st">"lr"</span>] = lr_schedule(global_step)

        <span class="cm"># 前向 + 蒸馏 Loss（teacher 在 forward 内部 no_grad 调用）</span>
        loss = model(observation, actions, <span class="var">teacher</span>=teacher_model)

        <span class="cm"># 反向 + 梯度裁剪 + 更新（仅 student 参数更新）</span>
        loss.backward()
        torch.nn.utils.clip_grad_norm_(model.parameters(), max_norm=<span class="num">1.0</span>)
        optim.step()
        optim.zero_grad(set_to_none=<span class="tp">True</span>)
</pre>

